---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Estimate Request Received | Great General LLC"
  description="Your estimate request has been received. Great General LLC will be in touch within one business day to schedule your free on-site visit."
  canonical="/contact-success"
  noindex={true}
>

<section class="success-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-card">
      <div class="success-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"/>
          <path d="M8 12l3 3 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1>Request Received</h1>
      <p class="success-lead">Thanks for reaching out to Great General LLC. Noel will review your request and be in touch within one business day — usually much sooner.</p>

      <div class="success-next">
        <h2>What Happens Next</h2>
        <div class="next-steps">
          <div class="next-step">
            <div class="next-num">1</div>
            <div>
              <strong>We'll contact you to schedule your free on-site estimate</strong>
              <p>Noel will reach out by phone or email to confirm the details of your project and schedule a convenient time to visit your property — anywhere on Maui, at no charge.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="next-step">
            <div class="next-num">2</div>
            <div>
              <strong>On-site visit and scope review</strong>
              <p>During the visit, we'll walk through the space, discuss your goals, and understand the full scope of the project. No high-pressure sales — just a clear look at what the project involves.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="next-step">
            <div class="next-num">3</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Written estimate</strong>
              <p>You'll receive a clear written estimate defining scope and pricing. No vague ballparks — a real number for a defined scope, so you can make an informed decision.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="success-contact">
        <p>Need to reach us sooner? Call or text Noel directly:</p>
        <a href="tel:8087954044" class="success-phone">(808) 795-4044</a>
        <a href="mailto:noel@greatgeneral.com" class="success-email">noel@greatgeneral.com</a>
      </div>

      <div class="success-actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-navy">Back to Home</a>
        <a href="/services/general-contracting" class="btn btn-outline-navy">View Our Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .success-section {
    background: var(--bg);
    min-height: calc(100vh - 68px - 360px);
    padding: 80px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .success-card {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .success-icon {
    width: 72px; height: 72px;
    background: rgba(14, 165, 78, .1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
    color: #0ea54e;
  }

  .success-card h1 { margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 38px); }

  .success-lead {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--slate);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .success-next {
    text-align: left;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--r);
    padding: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .success-next h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .next-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }

  .next-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .next-num {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .next-step strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .next-step p { font-size: 14px; margin: 0; }

  .success-contact {
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .success-contact p { color: var(--slate); margin-bottom: 12px; }

  .success-phone {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .success-email {
    display: block;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--slate);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .success-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-outline-navy {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--navy);
    color: var(--navy);
    padding: 14px 28px;
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: var(--r);
    display: inline-block;
    transition: opacity .15s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-outline-navy:hover { opacity: .75; }
</style>
